{"tid":2172043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德媒報導中國打算擴張勢力至 加勒比海地區，並形容為新殖民主義！！","createTime":"2020-08-24T10:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T01:25:56.000Z","uid":138409,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1069738bcc904c821690dcd9f2e0f52cbed95a04","tid":2172043,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"新聞來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RND_de/status/1297418794810273793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRND_de%2Fstatus%2F1297418794810273793&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=1ab161bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRND_de%2Fstatus%2F1297418794810273793&h=0a6d2ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RND_de/status/1297418794810273793</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rnd.de/resizer/zRfRM3ERcpE0gcNrvUFFFe7Dd0Q=/fit-in/1050x1050/filters:format(webp)/cloudfront-eu-central-1.images.arcpublishing.com/madsack/QSMBAQU5ABGJZOI5TFKCJEJUCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rnd.de%2Fresizer%2FzRfRM3ERcpE0gcNrvUFFFe7Dd0Q%3D%2Ffit-in%2F1050x1050%2Ffilters%3Aformat%28webp%29%2Fcloudfront-eu-central-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fmadsack%2FQSMBAQU5ABGJZOI5TFKCJEJUCI.jpg&h=243c5b62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n摘要：<br />\n- 德媒RND 引述嘅係荷蘭學者Tycho de Feijter嘅研究報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.atlcom.nl/upload/documenten/AP-3-2020-deFeijter.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atlcom.nl%2Fupload%2Fdocumenten%2FAP-3-2020-deFeijter.pdf&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=7a9ffa7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.atlcom.nl/upload/documenten/AP-3-2020-deFeijter.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n- 中國嘅目標係 <span class=\"gold\">荷屬安的列斯</span> （Netherlands Antilles）嗰堆島<br />\n<br />\n- 中國使用嘅策略，包括投資、小恩小惠 換取忠誠<br />\n- 中國依家提出投資1億2千萬美金，響 荷屬聖馬丁（其中一個島） 上面 起酒店同會議中心，打算日後擴張成為中國響加勒比嘅商業中心；亦都有越來越多中國人移居當地<br />\n<br />\n- 庫拉索（另外一個島）嘅首相 Eug&egrave;ne Rhuggenaath 承認，目前同中國洽談緊投資，指歐美投資者本身已經退卻，加上武漢肺炎，令到有更多空間畀中國投資者填補<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">- 中國嘅目標係美國，因為 荷屬安的列斯響正美國門口，可以打探美國動靜；甚至乎set埋雷達響嗰度監察美國艦隊動態</span>"},{"pid":"ef9ccabb2f77b3b1b20cb10a7183380258d958d2","tid":2172043,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:40:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bb4699772d445a909be85a1056d4640a6e3a5f50","tid":2172043,"uid":310817,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"幾時古巴導彈危機2.0?"},{"pid":"de0b2155c79d90fbe9669ff000868b0d58b72ec5","tid":2172043,"uid":13663,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"陳小春<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98619b23b3f4d13959880ed3ea974a797a944148","tid":2172043,"uid":79410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"呢D 真係殖民滲透計劃喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71298e1a6586ff4d8c1ea30a7757a15bf579bdfb","tid":2172043,"uid":24080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:43:12.000Z","msg":"幾時擴張致太陽系<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36c0a080ba146bf143df5340fac81162a2935f1","tid":2172043,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5adc032ddb98d353de5bbf221fab3118c3879753","tid":2172043,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"強國人食都無得食<br />\n仲俾錢收買d小國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf2bc0203cf88181584655adeda702b1501851e","tid":2172043,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0